title: Forest Sentinel Warwick

embed.description: Just a fun, quick little model mockup concept.

body:
Browsing through C&C, found [this thread](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/skin-champion-concepts/AGU1RtHn-victorious-fiora-artwork) which showcased Thomas Randby's work on Victorious Fiora, a concept art.

Kept scrolling through, found this idea, and although I'm not a Warwick player, I absolutely love it.

replies.body: Thanks so much!! I'm glad you like it!
